# phoneNumbers

**Instance Property**

An array of labeled phone numbers for a contact.

## Declaration

```swift
var phoneNumbers: [CNLabeledValue<CNPhoneNumber>] { get set }
```

## Discussion

This property is an array of [doc://com.apple.contacts/documentation/Contacts/CNLabeledValue] objects, each of which has a label and a [doc://com.apple.contacts/documentation/Contacts/CNPhoneNumber] value.
